    "Model trainingThe T5 model, which is a pre-trained transformer-based language model, is fine-tuned on the collected dataset.",
    "Fine-tuning involves training the model on the specific task of grammar and spelling correction using techniques like maximum likelihood estimation or sequence-to-sequence learning.",
